{
  "stem": "21582.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't need to hide anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it's amazing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I, I know every place under every cushion that I can crawl in to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CRYING] Not rational, but it's real.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] Can you describe for me the beginning of the war from your eyes?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How old were you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what do you remember from that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I just turned 10.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- I turned, turned 10-- turned-- in July.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the war started in September.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember the propaganda.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I, I remember the, the, the drumming up of the war, the, the, the, the preparation that I mentioned before-- the, the, the possibility of-- that the Germans are building up and threatening the invasion of Poland, and on the radios, trying to prepare and fortify.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and, and, and then the bombings started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, oh, we had these trial alarms, like sirens.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the sirens were repeated, the, the trial sirens, that when the real sirens sounded we didn't-- we didn't take it seriously.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember that my father was away on business-- not out of the city, but was not home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said, oh, it was real.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because the first bomb was dropped not far from where he was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
